cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper deals with large-scale industrial recommender systems and proposes a method to jointly learn the index structure and user preference prediction model. This involves techniques from information retrieval (IR), machine learning (LG), databases (DB), artificial intelligence (AI), and data structures (DS). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR, followed by cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.AI, and cs.DS.
